quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  23,75,"Sinndo Min Yurmino …ďe, Min hunci ko he…ďi …ďe kon immorde e lorra, …ďe duumotono e ndeer bewre ma…ď…ďe he…ďe wemmboo."
  23,76,"GooŇč…óii Min nanngirii …ďe Lepte …óen, …ďe koykinanaaki Joomi ma…ď…ďe …ďe yankinaaki."
  23,77,"Haa si Min ngudditii e dow ma…ď…ďe dammbugal marungal Lepte sa…ótu…óe, e jaka, kam…ďe e nyder …óum ko …ďe ta∆īii …ďe."
  23,78,"Ko KaŇčko woni On u…ó…óan∆äo on nan…óe …óen e gii…óe …óen e …ďer…óe …óen, fan…óii ko njeettoton."
  23,79,"Ko KaŇčko woni On Tak…óo on ka leydi ko fa'ade ka makko moo…ďoyte…óon."
  23,80,"Ko KaŇčko woni on mo no wurna O wara no woodani mo luutindirgol jemma on e √Īalawma on, enee, kaa on hakkiltah?"
  23,81,"Ko woni, …ďe mbii' yeru ko aram…ďe …ďe mb'inoo ko."
  23,82,"∆Āe mb'i: "Enee, si min maayii min ngonii mbullaari e ∆īi'e, hara minen ko min immintinoytee…ďe?""
  23,83,"GooŇč…óii min podanooma …óum minen e baabiraa…ďe amen ko adii, …óum wonaani si wonaa tinndi adinoo…ďe."
  23,84,"Maaku: "Ko hommbo leydi ndi woodani e …ďeen won…ďe e mayri, si tawii hi…óon nganndi?"
  23,85,"Aray …ďe mbi'a: "Ko Alla woodani" maaku: "Enee, on mbaajitotaako?""
  23,86,"Maaku: "Ko hommbo woni Jom kammuuji …óin jee…ói…ói e Jom Arsi mawki kin?""
  23,87,"Aray …ďe mbi'a: "Ko Alla" maaku: "Enee, on kulatah [Alla]?""
  23,88,"Maaku hommbo woni e Junngo Mu'um Laamu kala hu'unde hara KaŇčko homo walla O walletaake, si tawii on laatike ho…óon nganndi?"
  23,89,"Aray …ďe mbi'a: "Ko Alla woodani" maaku: "Enee, ko honno mbilirte…óon ?""